- ✅ **`[GeneratedRegex]` with downlevel fallback** — L12-27: proper conditional compilation with source-gen on .NET 7+ and `Compiled` on older TFMs.
- ✅ **`Concat(char, ReadOnlySpan<char>)` uses `stackalloc`** — L130-133: zero-heap span concat.
- ✅ **`FreestandingSpacingCharRegex` early-exit** — L55: avoids unnecessary processing.

